abstract: Jamaican sprinter Usain Bolt wins 200 meters at Golden Spike meet in Czech Republic.
lead_paragraph: Bolt finished in 20.13 seconds in his first race in Europe this year as he prepares for the world championships in August in Beijing.

headline.main: Usain Bolt Wins 200 Meters in Czech Republic
